'''Greta Thunberg''' (born 3 January 2003) is a [[Swedish]] climate activist. She is known for her strike outside  the [[Riksdag]] under the slogan ''School Strike for the climate''.<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.theguardian.com/science/2018/sep/01/swedish-15-year-old-cutting-class-to-fight-the-climate-crisis |title=The Swedish 15-year-old who's cutting class to fight the climate crisis |date=1 September 2018 |work=The Guardian}}</ref>

